reviewText: It was boring. I got tired of his code switching speech.
Could listen to his story telling all night! The last 20 minutes or so was a lot of justifiable anger, but lacked the infusion of humor.
Loved this!  Del is always great!
I enjoyed it for the most part ?
Wonderful to hear Del Shores tell about his life and the people in his life who inspired his writing and characters. After watching this I felt like I really became part of his crazy family!
